LXm.c		: Local Motif library (eg standard dialog's etc)
LXm.h		: Struct's and defines for the local Motif library
MANIFEST	: This file
Makefile	: Dummy Makefile to drive makegen
Makefile.tmpl	: Makegen template file
Minerva.h	: Depricated global header.
config.h.in	: GNU Autoconf input file for config.h
debug.c		: Multi-level debug routines.
debug.h		: Definitions for above
flock.c		: A reimplementation of flock() for sysV machines
portability.h	: Misc routines that may be missing on some boxes
site.h		: site specific configuration details
strlib.c	: General string handling routines that may not be available
ualarm.c	: A reimplementation of ualarm() in case it's not available
